Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.40,0:00:26.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- OKAY, THIS IS WEIRD.\NWHERE AM I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:35.62,Main,,0,0,0,,"THE RIVER STYX"?\NTHAT DOESN'T SOUND LIKE FUN.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:38.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- COME ON, AKIHISA.\NCOME TO OUR SIDE OF THE RIVER.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:42.21,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'S NICER THAN IT LOOKS.\NI PROMISE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:44.92,Main,,0,0,0,,- EVERYTHING IS\NBETTER OVER HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,- TRUST ME, THERE'S NO REASON\NFOR YOU TO BE SCARED, MAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:49.88,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS SIDE JUST TAKES\NA LITTLE GETTING USED TO.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.97,0:00:51.68,Main,,0,0,0,,NO BIG DEAL.\N- YUUJI?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:53.09,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT THE HELL ARE\NYOU DOING OVER THERE?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.18,0:00:55.01,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M HERE BECAUSE I'M HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:56.68,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S ALL GOOD.\NDON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.77,0:00:59.35,Main,,0,0,0,,THERE'S NO REASON FOR YOU\NTO BE SCARED, I PROMISE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:03.15,Main,,0,0,0,,COME ON OVER.  DON'T BE AFRAID.\NEVERYTHING IS FINE.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.23,0:01:04.69,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( screams )
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:11.20,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( singing in Japanese )
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:37.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( shivers )
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:45.96,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, WHERE ARE WE?\N- I DON'T REMEMBER EXACTLY.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:48.08,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I FEEL LIKE WE WENT\NTHROUGH HELL TO GET HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:49.67,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU HAD TO KNOW\NTHE GIRLS WOULD FIND OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.46,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT YOU WERE UP TO.\NI MEAN, IF YOU ASK ME,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:52.46,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU GUYS ARE LUCKY\NTO BE BREATHING.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:53.97,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:55.88,Main,,0,0,0,,WE SHOULD BE\NGONERS FOR SURE.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:00.06,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara: AKIHISA AND YUUJI\NMADE A CONTEST
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:02.06,Main,,0,0,0,,OUT OF HITTING ON\NCHICKS YESTERDAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:04.77,Main,,0,0,0,,THE GIRLS FOUND OUT AND\NPUNISHED THEM SOMEWHAT SEVERELY.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:06.27,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'VE NEVER SEEN\NSOMEONE PUNISHED
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:07.90,Main,,0,0,0,,AS GRUESOMELY AS YOU WERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:09.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I CAN HARDLY BEAR\NTO THINK ABOUT IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:11.40,Main,,0,0,0,,IT WAS JUST SO\NHORRIBLY SADISTIC.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.78,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, I'M GLAD\NI CAN'T REMEMBER IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:16.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- ME TOO, ALTHOUGH I GUESS\NWE DESERVED WHATEVER IT WAS.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:17.91,Main,,0,0,0,,WE WERE BEING JERKS.\N- I'M JUST SAYING,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:19.62,Main,,0,0,0,,THE NEXT TIME\NYOU'RE WITH GIRLS,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:21.74,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU SHOULD PROBABLY AVOID\NFLIRTING WITH OTHER GIRLS.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:24.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU KNOW, NOW THAT\NYOU MENTION IT,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:25.46,Main,,0,0,0,,WE MIGHT HAVE GOTTEN OFF\NA LITTLE EASY.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:27.08,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T KNOW\NIF I'D EXACTLY CALL
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:29.17,Main,,0,0,0,,A NEAR-DEATH EXPERIENCE\N"GETTING OFF EASY."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:30.96,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO, I WOULDN'T EITHER,\NBUT I THINK I GET
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:32.38,Main,,0,0,0,,WHERE AKI'S COMING FROM.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:34.13,Main,,0,0,0,,THERE MIGHT BE MORE\NPUNISHMENT TO COME.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.76,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO WHAT DO YOU\NTHINK WE SHOULD DO? RUN?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:37.01,Main,,0,0,0,,- Minami: SOMEONE SAY "RUN"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:41.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE'RE TOO LATE.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:46.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- Girls: TA DA!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:52.90,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, GIRLS.  YOU LOOK NICE,\NBUT WHY ARE YOU WEARING YUKATA?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:55.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- BECAUSE THEY'RE HOLDING\NA FESTIVAL IN TOWN, SILLY.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:01.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO, AKIHISA,\NWHAT DO YOU THINK?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:03.62,Main,,0,0,0,,- UM, THEY'RE GOOD.\NYOU GUYS LOOK SO NICE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:06.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- REALLY? THIS IS KINDA\NMY FIRST TIME WEARING ONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.21,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, YEAH, YOU\NGREW UP IN GERMANY.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:09.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I DON'T KNOW WHY\NI KEEP FORGETTING THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:16.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT? WILL YOU QUIT STARING?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.26,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasps ) OH.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:22.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I WAS JUST ZONING OUT.\N- OR MAYBE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:24.18,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU JUST COULDN'T\NKEEP YOUR EYES OFF HER.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.10,Main,,0,0,0,,MINAMI SURE DOES\NLOOK PRETTY, DOESN'T SHE?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:27.81,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:30.19,Main,,0,0,0,,- KIMONOS ARE SUPER GREAT\NBECAUSE THEY MAKE YOU LOOK GOOD
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:31.98,Main,,0,0,0,,EVEN IF YOU'VE\NGOT SMALL BOOBS.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:34.15,Main,,0,0,0,,- I STILL DON'T KNOW\NWHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:37.44,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, WELL, THEN I SUPPOSE\NI BETTER SHOW YOU, HUH?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:39.53,Main,,0,0,0,,PAY ATTENTION.\N( kisses )
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:43.82,Main,,0,0,0,,UH-OH.\N- HMM? ( screams )
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.91,0:04:45.12,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU SEE WHAT I MEAN?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.45,Main,,0,0,0,,HE LOST IT WAY FASTER\NTHAN USUAL.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:48.16,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:50.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- LISTEN, KOUTA,\NYOU'RE GONNA BE JUST FINE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:52.79,Main,,0,0,0,,STAY WITH ME NOW.\N- ( groans )
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:55.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I KNOW.  IT LOOKS\NA LOT WORSE THAN IT IS.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:57.71,Main,,0,0,0,,SO DON'T WORRY ABOUT ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:01.51,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:05.35,Main,,0,0,0,,HOW DO YOU LIKE MY YUKATA?\NTELL THE TRUTH.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:07.81,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'S FINE AND I ALWAYS\NTELL THE TRUTH, DON'T I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:10.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- THANK YOU.\NIN THAT CASE THEN,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:11.98,Main,,0,0,0,,WOULD YOU LIKE\NTO GET MARRIED?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:14.56,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO FREAKING WAY.\N- ALL RIGHT, THAN WOULD YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:16.61,Main,,0,0,0,,RATHER MOVE FORWARD\NBY GETTING ENGAGED FIRST?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:19.44,Main,,0,0,0,,- NOT EVEN A LITTLE.\N- THEN LET ME ASK YOU THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:21.36,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO MEANS NO.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:22.86,Main,,0,0,0,,- WOULD YOU LIKE\NTO KEEP BREATHING?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.12,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, OKAY FINE!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:25.74,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU LOOK GREAT, SHOUKO.\NVERY PRETTY.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:29.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT'S SO SWEET\NOF YOU TO SAY, YUUJI.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:30.91,Main,,0,0,0,,- LIKE YOU GAVE ME A CHOICE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:33.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- MY MOTHER ALWAYS TOLD ME\NTO DO WHATEVER IT TAKES
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:34.83,Main,,0,0,0,,TO KEEP MY MAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:41.09,Main,,0,0,0,,- THIS IS WEIRD. I THOUGHT\NTHEY WERE ALL MAD AT US.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:44.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I DON'T TRUST THIS,\NLIKE NOT AT ALL.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.64,Main,,0,0,0,,- OKAY, EVERYONE.\NARE WE ALL SET?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:49.89,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S TIME FOR US TO HEAD\NOVER TO THE FESTIVAL NOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:53.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- AKIRA'S RIGHT.\NLET'S GO GUYS.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:56.94,Main,,0,0,0,,HURRY UP, WE DON'T WANT\NTO BE LATE, DO WE?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M SO EXCITED RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:01.44,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS IS ONLY THE SECOND JAPANESE\NFESTIVAL I'VE BEEN TO.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:02.90,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T WANT\NTO MISS ANY OF IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:05.91,Main,,0,0,0,,- GET A MOVE ON, BOYS.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:08.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- Both: YEAH, OKAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:14.83,Main,,0,0,0,,- WOW, EVERYTHING\NIS SO SPARKLY.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- I KNOW, FOR REAL.\NI LOVE IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:18.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUMMY, SOMEONE HAS\NDONER KABOBS HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:21.55,Main,,0,0,0,,- THEY LOOK GOOD TOO.\N- WELL, WE SHOULD TRY THEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:23.26,Main,,0,0,0,,IF THEY LOOK GOOD,\NWHY NOT, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:25.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( screams )\N- YUP, MORE PUNISHMENT.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:28.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I WANT YOU TO GO\NBUY SOME FOR ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:29.93,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( screams )
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:33.69,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHY DID I HAVE\NTO AGREE WITH HER?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:35.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M GOING TO ASSUME\NYOU WANT SOME TOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:38.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I DON'T MIND PAYING FOR THEM.\N- IT'S FINE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:41.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I WON'T ARGUE WITH YOU.\NHOLD ON.  ARE YOU SERIOUS?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.90,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU'RE GONNA BUY THEM?\N- WHAT'S WRONG?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:46.74,Main,,0,0,0,,DID YOU WANT TO PAY INSTEAD?\N- NO, NO, AS YOU WERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:50.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I WONDER.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:52.91,Main,,0,0,0,,MAYBE SHE REALLY\NDID FORGIVE ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:55.75,Main,,0,0,0,,- HERE IT IS.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:58.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I GOT US ONE ORDER TO SPLIT\NIF THAT'S OKAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:07:00.17,Main,,0,0,0,,THERE ARE A LOT OF THINGS HERE\NI WANT TO TRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.84,Main,,0,0,0,,SO I DIDN'T WANT\NTO FILL UP TOO SOON.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:04.34,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, GOOD PLAN.\NI'M TOTALLY COOL WITH THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.51,Main,,0,0,0,,SO HOW DOES IT TASTE?\N- OH, I CAN'T EAT AND WALK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:07.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M NOT SURE YET.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I GUESS THEY DON'T\NUSE LAMB IN JAPAN,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:13.48,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT IT'S STILL PRETTY YUMMY.\NYOU TRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:15.14,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU MIGHT ACTUALLY LIKE IT\NBETTER THIS WAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:20.06,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH WOW, THIS IS REALLY GOOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:22.19,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, AKI, YOUR FACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:24.32,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU'VE GOT SOME SAUCE ON IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:29.57,Main,,0,0,0,,- THANKS, THAT WAS NICE\NAND AWKWARD.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:32.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- AKIHISA, I JUST BOUGHT\NSOME OCTOPUS DUMPLINGS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.20,Main,,0,0,0,,WOULD YOU LIKE TO TRY SOME?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:36.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, YEAH, OF COURSE I WOULD.\NTHANKS, HIMEJI.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:37.71,Main,,0,0,0,,ONE DUMPLING PLEASE.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:41.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- HERE YOU GO.\NSAY AAH.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.42,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT'S WRONG?\NI THOUGHT YOU WANTED ONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:44.71,Main,,0,0,0,,DOES IT NOT LOOK GOOD?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:48.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT LOOKS FINE.\NIT'S NOT THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:51.51,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, THEN.  AAH.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- AAH.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,MHMM, YUM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:56.60,Main,,0,0,0,,THE PANCAKE PART\NIS HOT AND CREAMY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:58.48,Main,,0,0,0,,AND THE OCTOPUS\NIS NICE AND CHEWY.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:08:00.36,Main,,0,0,0,,( gasps )\NNO WAIT, AKIRA!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:02.27,Main,,0,0,0,,PLEASE! I KNOW\NTHAT SOUNDED SEXUAL,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:03.82,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT IT WASN'T AT ALL.\NI SWEAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:06.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- "THE OCTOPUS IS CHEWY,"\NTHAT'S SEXUAL?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:07.82,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'S NOT?\N- ARE YOU TRYING TO SAY
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:10.07,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU DIDN'T LIKE IT?\N- NO.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:12.99,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT'D YOU SCREW UP, AKI,\NTHIS TIME?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:15.08,Main,,0,0,0,,QUIT FREAKING OUT.\NIT'S JUST A FESTIVAL.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:16.95,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU CAN BE SUCH\NA BABY SOMETIMES.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:18.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHO'S FREAKING OUT?\NYOU'RE THE ONE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:19.92,Main,,0,0,0,,SHELLING OUT\NAT EVERY BOOTH.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, YOU DON'T KNOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:23.13,Main,,0,0,0,,THESE COULD HAVE BEEN\NTOTALLY FREE, GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:24.92,Main,,0,0,0,,- THIS IS ONLY YOUR\NSECOND FESTIVAL HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.67,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S OKAY IF YOU COULDN'T\NHELP YOURSELF.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:29.01,Main,,0,0,0,,- THANK YOU.  COTTON CANDY\NIS LIKE WAY DELICIOUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.22,Main,,0,0,0,,DO YOU WANT TO TRY SOME, AKI?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:38.68,Main,,0,0,0,,SURE, I LOVE THAT STUFF.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:41.06,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, YOU DO.\NSAY AHH.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:43.36,Main,,0,0,0,,- AAH.\N- IT'S GOOD, AM I RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, IT'S GOOD.\NTHANKS, MINAMI.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:48.65,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, YOU'RE WELCOME.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:51.41,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI, WOULD YOU LIKE\NSOME OF MY NOODLES?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:54.03,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, SURE. I GUESS I'LL\NHAVE SOME IF YOU DON'T MIND.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:55.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- I HAVE OKONOMIYAKI TOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:57.70,Main,,0,0,0,,- THANKS, THAT'S\NVERY NICE OF YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.46,Main,,0,0,0,,- WOULD YOU LIKE SOME SODA?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:01.25,Main,,0,0,0,,- YES, MUCH APPRECIATED.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:04.34,Main,,0,0,0,,- NICE, YUUJI LOOKS LIKE\NHE GOT OFF THE HOOK TOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:05.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I MEAN, THIS IS A FESTIVAL.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:07.34,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY WOULD THEY WANT\NTO BE PISSED THE WHOLE TIME?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:08.72,Main,,0,0,0,,TODAY ROCKS!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:11.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- AKIHISA,\NTHEY HAVE BABY CHICKENS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:12.93,Main,,0,0,0,,IN DIFFERENT COLORS OVER THERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:15.55,Main,,0,0,0,,THERE'S LIKE GREEN ONES,\NAND BLUE ONES, AND EVERYTHING.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:18.48,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, THEY JUST HIRE SOMEONE\NTO PAINT THE BABIES.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:20.56,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT'S NOT TRUE.\NIT'S BECAUSE OF THEIR BREED
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:22.81,Main,,0,0,0,,OR SOMETHING NATURAL LIKE THAT.\N- ( laughs )
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:25.11,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU TWO ARE LIKE\NBEYOND STUPID.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:27.02,Main,,0,0,0,,KOUTA, WHAT DO YOU THINK\NABOUT ALL THIS?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:32.32,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( screeches )
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( evil chuckle )
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:36.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I'LL COLOR YOU\NHOWEVER I LIKE!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:40.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, PAINTING MAKES\NA SICK KIND OF SENSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:43.04,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO TELL ME, AKI, ARE YOU\NHAVING A GOOD TIME YET?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUP.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.46,Main,,0,0,0,,- AND, YUUJI, ARE\NYOU HAVING FUN?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:48.21,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUP, SURE AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:49.92,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, LOOK, AKIHISA.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:52.30,Main,,0,0,0,,IT TURNS OUT THE FESTIVAL\NIS THROWING A SPECIAL EVENT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:54.01,Main,,0,0,0,,LATER ON TODAY.\N- "ENTER TO WIN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:56.55,Main,,0,0,0,,OUR FIRST EVER SUMMER\NMISS YUKATA BEAUTY PAGEANT."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:58.18,Main,,0,0,0,,NICE.\N- BEAUTY PAGEANT?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:09:59.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE SHOULD TOTALLY\NGO WATCH THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:01.56,Main,,0,0,0,,- MY CAMERA AND I\NARE UP FOR IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:03.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- ALL RIGHTY THEN.\NHOW ABOUT WE ALL GO.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:04.65,Main,,0,0,0,,- BETTER YET,\NWHY DON'T WE HAVE EVERYONE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:05.65,Main,,0,0,0,,JUST COMPETE IN THE THING.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:10.15,Main,,0,0,0,,WELL, I MEAN, YOU DON'T\NHAVE TO OBVIOUSLY.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:12.20,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I JUST THOUGHT\NIT'D BE A NICE MEMORY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:14.99,Main,,0,0,0,,OF THE DAY AND STUFF.\NTHAT'S ALL.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:17.37,Main,,0,0,0,,- GREAT IDEA.\N- WHAT? REALLY?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:19.62,Main,,0,0,0,,- YES, OF COURSE, WE SHOULD\NALL DO THIS TOGETHER.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:22.50,Main,,0,0,0,,- SOMETHING WE ARE SURE\NTO NEVER FORGET.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:25.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- ALL RIGHT, LET'S\NCOMPETE IN THE PAGEANT.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:28.09,Main,,0,0,0,,LET'S HAVE\NEVERYONE HERE COMPETE.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:29.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- Both: RUN!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:38.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( screams )
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:40.85,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHERE ARE YOU OFF TO\NIN SUCH A HURRY? YOU SCARED?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:43.27,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE'RE GOING TO PARTICIPATE\NIN THE BEAUTY PAGEANT.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,ISN'T THAT RIGHT, YUUJI?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:45.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT? DON'T TAKE\NTHIS PERSONALLY,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:48.23,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT YOU GUYS AREN'T\NMAKING ANY SENSE LIKE AT ALL.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:51.03,Main,,0,0,0,,- FOR REAL.\NWHAT THE HELL IS GOING ON?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:53.90,Main,,0,0,0,,- HITTING ON GIRLS EARLIER.\N- SURELY YOU DIDN'T BELIEVE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.99,0:10:55.61,Main,,0,0,0,,WE WERE FINISHED\NWITH YOU BOYS YET.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.41,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU SHOULD KNOW BY NOW\NTHAT WE WOULD MAKE YOU PAY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:59.03,Main,,0,0,0,,SEVERELY FOR WHAT YOU DID.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:01.62,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( laughs )\NHEY, BOYS, DON'T WORRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:03.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I TOTALLY BROUGHT\NMY MAKEUP KIT WITH ME TONIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:05.08,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( both gasp )\N- NO WAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:07.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M SUPER TALL.\NI'D NEVER PASS AS A WOMAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:09.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I THINK MAKING AKIHISA\NDRESS UP AS A CHICK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:10.92,Main,,0,0,0,,IS PUNISHMENT ENOUGH\NFOR BOTH OF US.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.96,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT?! DON'T YOU USE ME\NTO TRY TO GET OUT THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:14.42,Main,,0,0,0,,IF ANYONE'S DRESSING UP,\NIT'S YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:15.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- PLEASE STOP FIGHTING.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.34,Main,,0,0,0,,NEITHER ONE OF YOU\NIS GOING TO WIN.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:18.97,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU GUYS SHOULD\NFOLLOW KOUTA'S LEAD.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:21.06,Main,,0,0,0,,HE'S TAKING HIS\NCROSS-DRESSING LIKE A MAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:22.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( sighs )
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:25.85,Main,,0,0,0,,- I THINK THIS IS WHAT THEY MEAN\NBY "CRUEL AND UNUSUAL."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:30.65,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M SORRY.  I HAVE SUCH\NA FLARE FOR THE DRAMATIC.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I PROBABLY OVERDID IT\NWITH THE MAKEUP,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:34.69,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:37.70,Main,,0,0,0,,- I JUST WISH HE WEREN'T\NSO EXCITED ABOUT DOING IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:41.95,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T LIKE THIS AT ALL.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:46.33,Main,,0,0,0,,WHERE'D THEY COME UP\NWITH KOUMI? I HATE IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:49.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH PLEASE.  WHAT ARE\NYOU COMPLAINING ABOUT?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:51.00,Main,,0,0,0,,ON TOP OF LOOKING LIKE\NA TOTAL FREAK,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:52.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M SUPPOSED TO ACT\NLIKE A DAMN FOREIGNER.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.76,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, THE ONLY WAY\NANYONE WOULD EVER BELIEVE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:56.63,Main,,0,0,0,,SOMEONE AS BIG AS YOU WAS\NA CHICK IS IF YOU TELL THEM
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:58.22,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU'RE AN INTERNATIONAL ATHLETE.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:01.76,Main,,0,0,0,,- EVERY SINGLE ONE OF YOU\NLOOKS JUST ADORABLE.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:04.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT'S RIGHT.  ONE OF YOU\NCOULD TOTALLY WIN THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:06.02,Main,,0,0,0,,- I CAN'T TELL YOU\NHOW HAPPY IT MAKES ME
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:08.52,Main,,0,0,0,,TO SEE MY LITTLE BROTHER GROW UP\NTO BE SUCH A PRETTY GIRL.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:09.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- I CAN'T TELL YOU\NHOW NOT HAPPY
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:11.27,Main,,0,0,0,,IT MAKES ME\NTO HEAR YOU SAY THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:15.32,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU NEED TO WORK ON\NYOUR SEX APPEAL, YUUJI.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:17.57,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DO NOT.\NI'M SEXY AS HELL.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:20.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, I HAVE A QUESTION.\NI DIDN'T DO ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:22.78,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY DO I HAVE TO\NCOMPETE IN THE PAGEANT?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:24.54,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara: BECAUSE THAT'S\NTHE PLOT IN THIS EPISODE.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:25.95,Main,,0,0,0,,ROLL WITH IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.67,Main,,0,0,0,,- Mizuki: BAKA AND TEST.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.01,Main,,0,0,0,,- Announcer: AND NOW,\NIT'S TIME TO START
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:40.26,Main,,0,0,0,,OUR FIRST EVER SUMMER\NMISS YUKATA BEAUTY CONTEST.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:42.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( cheers )
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:46.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- AS A COMMENTATOR,\NWE HAVE MR. OBATA,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:48.85,Main,,0,0,0,,WHO'S WEARING\NHIS YUKATA TODAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.81,Main,,0,0,0,,HE IS ALSO OUR\NSPONSOR AND JUDGE.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:53.06,Main,,0,0,0,,- I AM EXCITED TO BE,\NBUT I'M EVEN MORE EXCITED
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:54.82,Main,,0,0,0,,TO SEE ALL THE PRETTY LADIES.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:58.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE GONNA DO GREAT.\NI JUST KNOW IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:02.12,Main,,0,0,0,,- STOP STRESSING.  NO ONE\NWILL FIND OUT THE TRUTH.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.70,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI, IF YOU BELIEVE\NIN YOURSELF, YOU CAN WIN.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:06.75,Main,,0,0,0,,- ARE YOU KIDDING ME?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'LL RECORD THE WHOLE THING.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:11.25,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS TIME YOU'RE\NTHE ONE ON CAMERA.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:13.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- I HATE YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.21,Main,,0,0,0,,- Aki: DUDE, WHAT ARE\NWE GONNA DO?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:18.88,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuuji: WE MAKE SURE\NWE LOSE THIS THING FAST.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:20.97,Main,,0,0,0,,THEN WE ROLL.\N- I GOT IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:22.22,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY DON'T WE JUST\NTELL THEM WE'RE GUYS?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE CAN'T DO THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:25.14,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, LIKE ABSOLUTELY CAN'T.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:27.06,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT IF SOMEONE WE KNOW,\NLIKE SOMEONE FROM SCHOOL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:28.85,Main,,0,0,0,,IS IN THE AUDIENCE?\N- THINK ABOUT IT
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.64,Main,,0,0,0,,FOR JUST A SECOND.\NIMAGINE OUR CLASS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:32.27,Main,,0,0,0,,FOUND OUT WE WERE\NDRESSED UP LIKE CHICKS.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:34.48,Main,,0,0,0,,AND NOT ONLY WERE WE DOLLED UP\NFROM HEAD TO TOE,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:36.15,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT WE WERE SO CONFIDENT\NIN OUR HOTNESS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.90,Main,,0,0,0,,WE ACTUALLY ENTERED\NA CONTEST TO PROVE IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:41.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO, THAT'S SOCIAL SUICIDE!\NI FINALLY GOT POPULAR!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:42.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I CAN'T GO BACK\NTO BEING A NOBODY.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:43.99,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE IDEA OF\NPOPULAR AND MINE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:45.45,Main,,0,0,0,,ARE TWO DIFFERENT THINGS.\N- FOCUS!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:46.74,Main,,0,0,0,,THERE'S ONLY ONE WAY\NWE'RE GONNA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:48.45,Main,,0,0,0,,GET OUT OF THIS\NMASSIVE BALL OF SUCK.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:50.66,Main,,0,0,0,,WE CAN'T ALLOW OURSELVES\NTO MAKE IT PAST THE FIRST ROUND.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:52.33,Main,,0,0,0,,AND NO ONE CAN FIND OUT\NWE'RE GUYS.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:59.46,Main,,0,0,0,,OUR TIME HAS COME.\NTHIS IS OUR BATTLE FOR MANHOOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:06.47,Main,,0,0,0,,- FIRST UP TONIGHT, WE HAVE\NLOVELY CONTESTANT NUMBER ONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:07.72,Main,,0,0,0,,PLEASE TAKE THE STAGE.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:12.81,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( cheers )
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:15.19,Main,,0,0,0,,- OKAY, WHAT DO I DO NOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:17.02,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, SWEETIE, WANT\NTO TELL US YOUR NAME?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:20.99,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'LL JUST LOOK AT THE FLOOR\NAND BE AS QUIET AS I CAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:23.07,Main,,0,0,0,,( high-pitch )\NUM, HELLO.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:24.74,Main,,0,0,0,,MY NAME IS AKIKO YOSHII.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:26.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- PERFECT.  NOW IT SOUNDS LIKE\NYOU MIGHT BE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:28.49,Main,,0,0,0,,A LITTLE BIT SHY, MISS AKIKO.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:31.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHYNESS USUALLY MEANS\NA GIRL IS PURE AND INNOCENT.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:32.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M GOING TO GIVE\NHER A HIGH SCORE.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:33.62,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHY?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:35.25,Main,,0,0,0,,- DO YOU HAVE ANY\NSPECIAL TALENTS?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:37.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- I CAN'T LIE ABOUT THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:39.42,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT IF THEY START ASKING ME\NQUESTIONS ABOUT THE TALENT?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.46,Main,,0,0,0,,( high pitch )\NI GUESS I'D HAVE TO SAY COOKING.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:44.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M GOOD AT PAELLA AND\NSPAGHETTI CARBONARA TOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:46.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO DO YOU MOSTLY\NCOOK AT HOME?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:48.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- UH-HUH, I COOK ALMOST\NEVERY SINGLE DAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,- A LOOKER AND A COOKER.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:52.23,Main,,0,0,0,,DON'T SEE THAT MUCH\NTHESE DAYS.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:53.77,Main,,0,0,0,,NOW TELL US, DO YOU\NHAVE A BOYFRIEND?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:56.06,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO! NO BOYFRIEND!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:57.44,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( cheers )\N- WELL, THAT IS GOOD NEWS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:59.27,Main,,0,0,0,,FOR ALL THE GUYS\NIN THE AUDIENCE.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:01.69,Main,,0,0,0,,MR. OBATA, WHAT'S\NYOUR OPINION ON THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:03.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- IF YOU GIVE ME YOUR PHONE\NNUMBER AND LET ME CALL YOU,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:05.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I PROMISE TO GIVE YOU MONEY\NTO SPEND ON WHATEVER YOU WANT.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:08.41,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO YOU KNOW, I'D LIKE\NTO PUNCH HIM FOR SAYING THAT,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:10.49,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT HE IS OUR SPONSOR.\NNOW, MISS AKIKO,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:12.04,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT DO YOU LIKE MOST
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:13.83,Main,,0,0,0,,ABOUT THE YUKATA YOU'RE\NWEARING FOR US TODAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:16.25,Main,,0,0,0,,- LIKE ABOUT IT?\NWELL, IT'S VERY MODEST.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:18.50,Main,,0,0,0,,SO IT HIDES MY BODY.\N- INTERESTING.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:21.09,Main,,0,0,0,,SO THEN, MR. OBATA,\NHAVE ANY QUESTIONS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:23.55,Main,,0,0,0,,ABOUT HER MANNER\NOF WEARING YUKATA?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:26.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- YES, I DO.  I WANT TO KNOW\NIF SHE'S WEARING ANY UNDERWEAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:29.85,Main,,0,0,0,,- UNDERWEAR? LIKE PANTIES?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:31.89,Main,,0,0,0,,( high pitch ) NO FREAKIN' WAY!\NI DON'T WEAR THAT STUFF!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:35.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( cheering )
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:38.69,Main,,0,0,0,,- THANK YOU FOR ANSWERING THAT\NWILDLY INAPPROPRIATE QUESTION.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:40.23,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU CAN LEAVE THE STAGE NOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:46.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- NICE SCORE, MAN.\NTHEY LIKE YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- I HATE YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:53.62,Main,,0,0,0,,- PLEASE TELL US YOUR NAME.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:56.16,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, OKAY.\NI AM KOUMI TSUCHIYA.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:57.96,Main,,0,0,0,,- AND DID YOU COME HERE\NTO SWIM TODAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:00.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DID.\N- GREAT, NEXT QUESTION.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:02.59,Main,,0,0,0,,DO YOU OFTEN WEAR YUKATA?\N- I DON'T.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:05.09,Main,,0,0,0,,- DID YOU COME HERE ALONE\NOR ARE YOU HERE WITH FRIENDS?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:07.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- WITH FRIENDS.\N- SO ARE THEY CHEERING YOU ON
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:09.51,Main,,0,0,0,,IN THE AUDIENCE?\N- NO, THEY'RE NOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:11.55,Main,,0,0,0,,- HMM.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:14.93,Main,,0,0,0,,OKAY, BESIDES YUKATA, WHAT ARE\NYOUR FAVORITE KINDS OF CLOTHING?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:17.89,Main,,0,0,0,,- SILK CHINESE DRESSES, KIMONOS,\NAN OUTFIT FOR RACECAR GIRLS,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:19.44,Main,,0,0,0,,CHEERLEADERS, NURSES,\NFLIGHT ATTENDANTS,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:21.36,Main,,0,0,0,,WAITRESSES AT OLD-SCHOOL DINERS,\NAND POLICE WOMEN.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.44,Main,,0,0,0,,ALSO, ANY KIND OF LEOTARD,\NCHICK POWER SUITS,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:25.74,Main,,0,0,0,,AND SCHOOL GIRL UNIFORM,\NSHRINE MAIDEN OUTFITS,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.45,Main,,0,0,0,,MAID UNIFORMS,\NAND TENNIS OUTFITS.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:31.03,Main,,0,0,0,,UH, I MEAN, NOTHING MUCH.\N- ( cheering )
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:32.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, THAT WAS UNEXPECTED.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:34.12,Main,,0,0,0,,APPARENTLY THE SHORT-ANSWER\NSWEETHEART
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:35.91,Main,,0,0,0,,ENJOYS COSTUMES ALMOST AS MUCH
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:38.71,Main,,0,0,0,,AS THE AUDIENCE ENJOYS HER.\N- NO, FORGET I SAID ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:41.88,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( cheers )
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:44.17,Main,,0,0,0,,- PLEASE CALM DOWN.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.75,Main,,0,0,0,,- THIS IS QUITE A REACTION.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS CUTIE'S DEFINITELY\NMAKING IT TO THE FINALS.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:51.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- PLEASE STOP.\NYOU DON'T HAVE TO CHEER FOR ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:52.85,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( cheers )
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:54.05,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( sighs )
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:59.06,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOUR PLAN BACKFIRE\NON YOU, KOUMI?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:01.65,Main,,0,0,0,,- I HATE YOU AND\NI HATE THIS PLACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:05.15,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( with accent )\NI'M HONG XIONG LI.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:08.03,Main,,0,0,0,,IT IS SO NICE TO MEET YOU ALL.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:10.90,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE MIGHT HAVE A REAL-LIFE\NAMAZONIAN WOMAN ON OUR HANDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:13.49,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT DO YOU THINK, MR. OBATA?\N- I LOVE THE TALL ONES.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:15.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M ENTRANCED.\NSOME MIGHT CALL IT A FETISH,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.16,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT IT'S SIMPLY A RESPECT\NFOR STRONG WOMEN.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:18.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:19.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHE HAS THE HIGHEST SCORE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:21.25,Main,,0,0,0,,OF ALL OF OUR\NCONTESTANTS SO FAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:23.71,Main,,0,0,0,,NOW THEN, DO YOU HAVE ANY--\NWHERE'RE YOU GOING?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:25.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE'LL BE MARRIED IN THE SPRING
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:26.55,Main,,0,0,0,,AND SPEND OUR HONEYMOON\NIN CAMBODIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:28.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE'RE FROM DIFFERENT CULTURES.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:29.42,Main,,0,0,0,,OUR FAMILIES WOULD\NNEVER APPROVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:32.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- THE FORBIDDEN ASPECT\NOF OUR LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:34.72,Main,,0,0,0,,ONLY MAKES IT STRONGER.\NDO YOU NOT AGREE, DEAR?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:36.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT LOVE? WHAT ARE\NYOU TALKING ABOUT?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:39.14,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'LL FEEL THE SAME WAY I DO\NSOMEDAY.  JUST HAVE FAITH.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:40.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( normal ) THE ONLY THING\NI HAVE FAITH IN
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.10,Main,,0,0,0,,IS THAT I'M ABOUT\NTO KICK YOUR ASS.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:43.65,Main,,0,0,0,,- THERE'S NO NEED\NTO BE AFRAID, DARLING!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:45.32,Main,,0,0,0,,WE CAN START OFF AS FRIENDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:46.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I'LL TAKE CARE OF YOU\NFOR THE REST OF YOUR LIFE.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:48.53,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU'LL WANT FOR NOTHING!\N- ENOUGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:51.07,Main,,0,0,0,,DON'T SAY I DIDN'T WARN YOU.\NYOU ASKED FOR IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:53.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- ASKED FOR IT?\NI'M PRACTICALLY BEGGING FOR IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.28,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU COULD DO\NANYTHING YOU WANT?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:57.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- AFFAIRS WILL\NNOT BE PERMITTED.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.12,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHOUKO, NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:01.75,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT ABOUT ANY OF THIS\NIS AN AFFAIR?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:03.12,Main,,0,0,0,,( cries )
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:12.05,Main,,0,0,0,,- I THINK I'M GONNA\NNEED THERAPY NOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:13.55,Main,,0,0,0,,- ON THE BRIGHT SIDE,\NYOU COULD SAY WE HAD
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:14.93,Main,,0,0,0,,AN UNFORGETTABLE SUMMER.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.68,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, EXCEPT\NI WANT TO FORGET IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:19.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT WAS PROBABLY FOR THE BEST\NTHE CONTEST GOT CANCELLED.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:20.97,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T THINK THAT\NCREEPY SPONSOR GUY
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.06,0:18:22.18,Main,,0,0,0,,WOULD AGREE WITH YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:24.19,Main,,0,0,0,,- HUH, MAYBE WE WENT\NA TEENSY BIT OVERBOARD.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:26.15,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT DO YOU THINK? SHOULD\NWE LET THEM OFF THE HOOK NOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:27.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- PERHAPS.\NI'M NOT OPPOSED TO IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:30.03,Main,,0,0,0,,- THEY ALL LOOK PRETTY SORRY\NIF YOU ASK ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:31.36,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY DON'T WE\NMAKE AN EXCEPTION
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.65,Main,,0,0,0,,AND FORGIVE THEM\NTHIS TIME, OKAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:34.32,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( sighing )
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:36.57,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU KNOW, I WONDER WHO WOULD\NHAVE WON THE PAGEANT
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:38.45,Main,,0,0,0,,IF IT DIDN'T GET ALL EXPLODED.\NDON'T YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:41.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T KNOW.  HIDEYOSHI SEEMS\NTHE MOST APPROPRIATE CHOICE.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:44.16,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T UNDERSTAND.  WHY AM I\NTHE MOST APPROPRIATE CHOICE?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:46.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M A GUY TOO.\NAND YOU HAD THE HIGHEST SCORE.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:48.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- MY HEART DID A LITTLE\NFLUTTER-THING WHEN I SAW
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:49.96,Main,,0,0,0,,KOUTA DRESSED UP\NLIKE A GIRL.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:52.42,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT ABOUT YOU, AKIRA?\N- IT WAS FUN.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:54.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I MEAN, I'M USED TO AKI\NWEARING GIRL'S CLOTHES,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:56.43,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT IT WAS STILL NICE\NTO SEE THE OTHER TWO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:58.05,Main,,0,0,0,,EMBRACE THEIR\NCROSS-DRESSING SELVES.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:18:59.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT ARE YOU\NTALKING ABOUT, CRAZY?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:01.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I DON'T EVER\NWEAR CHICK CLOTHING!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:03.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, DON'T BE RIDICULOUS,\NAKI, MY DARLING.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:05.52,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU WORE A SKIRT AGAIN\NLAST NIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:07.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I SWEAR YOU HAVE\NTHE WORST MEMORY.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,OF COURSE, YOU WERE\NASLEEP AT THE TIME.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:11.07,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE MY SISTER!\NWHAT DID YOU DO TO ME
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:13.28,Main,,0,0,0,,WHILE I WAS SLEEPING?!\N- AKI, CALM DOWN.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:15.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I AM HALFWAY LYING\NABOUT THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:18.41,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT IS THAT SUPPOSED\NTO MEAN, YOU SCHIZO?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:20.33,Main,,0,0,0,,TELL THE TRUTH.\NWHAT DID YOU DO TO ME?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:22.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING.\NI COULDN'T GET IT UP
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:24.41,Main,,0,0,0,,PAST YOUR KNEES.\N- SO YOU LEFT IT HALFWAY ON?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:27.79,Main,,0,0,0,,- IF YOU'D RATHER, WE CAN SAY\NIT WAS HALFWAY OFF INSTEAD.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:30.21,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( cries )\N- Yuuji: OKAY, GUYS.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:31.92,Main,,0,0,0,,THE FOOD'S READY.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:34.05,Main,,0,0,0,,- All: YEAH, I'M STARVING.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:36.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- THIS LOOKS SO DELICIOUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:38.89,Main,,0,0,0,,- SERIOUSLY, SAKAMOTO\NIS REALLY GOOD AT GRILLING.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:40.93,Main,,0,0,0,,- MY FUTURE HUSBAND,\NI'M SO PROUD.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:44.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- I WANTED TO COOK TOO, BUT\NAKIHISA WOULDN'T LET ME HELP.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:46.73,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S NOT LIKE I WAS GONNA\NACCIDENTLY KILL SOMEONE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:48.48,Main,,0,0,0,,WITH A KITCHEN KNIFE.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:50.61,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT WASN'T WHAT\NWE WERE AFRAID OF, HIMEJI.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.69,0:19:52.61,Main,,0,0,0,,THE PROBLEM WAS\NYOU COULD STILL HAVE KILLED US
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:54.36,Main,,0,0,0,,WITHOUT EVEN TOUCHING A KNIFE.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:56.40,Main,,0,0,0,,- IF SHE COOKS, WE'RE DEAD.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:58.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- MY TONGUE JUST CURLED\NBACK IN MY THROAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:01.03,Main,,0,0,0,,- THE WOMAN CANNOT BE\NALLOWED NEAR A KITCHEN.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:03.91,Main,,0,0,0,,- I HAVE AN IDEA.  WHY DON'T\NWE HAVE A COOKING COMPETITION
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:06.16,Main,,0,0,0,,BETWEEN ALL THE GIRLS.\NAND THE GUYS CAN JUDGE IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:08.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- Boys: THAT'S\NTHE WORST IDEA EVER.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:10.88,Main,,0,0,0,,- OOH, I LIKE IT,\NBUT COOKING'S SO SUBJECTIVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:12.09,Main,,0,0,0,,HOW DO WE DECIDE\NWHO THE WINNER IS?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:16.30,Main,,0,0,0,,- IF THEY'RE GOING\NFOR A K.O,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:17.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I'D KNOW WHO'D WIN.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:22.97,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( groans )\N- GOOD GRIEF.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:24.72,Main,,0,0,0,,WE SURE DID STUFF OUR FACES,\NDIDN'T WE?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:27.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE DID, YEAH.\NCALL ME CRAZY, THOUGH.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:28.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M STILL HUNGRY.\N- TOO BAD.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:29.77,Main,,0,0,0,,THERE'S NO FOOD\NLEFT TO COOK.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:31.44,Main,,0,0,0,,- SURE THERE IS, MAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:33.86,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S RIGHT IN FRONT OF YOU.\N- ALL I SEE IS UGLY.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:35.78,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'S CALLED THE OCEAN,\NYOU NIMROD.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:38.20,Main,,0,0,0,,FRESH CLAMS ARE TOTALLY OUT OF\NTHIS WORLD WHEN THEY'RE GRILLED.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:39.45,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH YEAH.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:43.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- Mizuki: YOU KNOW,\NNOW THAT I THINK OF IT...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:45.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:47.83,Main,,0,0,0,,- I BAKED SOME\NMADELEINES AT HOME.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.50,Main,,0,0,0,,SO WE COULD EAT\NTHOSE IF YOU WANTED.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:51.79,Main,,0,0,0,,- COME ON, YUUJI.\NLET'S GO FIND US SOME CLAMS.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:53.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, CLAMS!\NCLAMS ARE GOOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:54.67,Main,,0,0,0,,WE SHOULD FIND SOME.\NWE SHOULD GET SO MANY
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:56.26,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT WE'LL NEVER BE ABLE\NTO EAT THEM ALL.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:59.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, SO WOULD YOU LIKE\NTO JOIN ME ON THE BEACH, KOUTA?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.22,0:21:01.93,Main,,0,0,0,,WE CAN HELP THEM.\N- YES, I LOVE CLAMS.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:03.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- WEIRD, I WONDER\NWHAT THAT WAS ALL ABOUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:05.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- THERE'S NO TELLING.\N- THEY'RE GUYS.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:07.52,Main,,0,0,0,,SO WHAT'S THE STORY\NWITH THOSE MADELEINES?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.85,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, YEAH, WELL,\NI DID BAKE A DOZEN OF THEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.94,0:21:11.56,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I FORGOT THAT\NI FORGOT TO BRING THEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:13.48,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY'RE STILL SITTING AT HOME.\N- BUMMER,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:15.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I WAS LOOKING FORWARD\NTO SOMETHING SWEET.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:17.65,Main,,0,0,0,,- Hideyoshi: WE CAN DO\NTHIS, GUYS. WE HAVE TO.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:19.99,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T WANT TO DIE!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( singing in Japanese )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:57.59,Main,,0,0,0,,- Minami: LOOK AT THEM.  THEY'RE\NSLEEPING LIKE LITTLE BABIES.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.67,0:22:59.25,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, CONSIDERING\NWHO THEY ARE,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.34,0:23:01.51,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT SEEMS FAIRLY APPROPRIATE.\N- YEAH, RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.59,0:23:03.09,Main,,0,0,0,,WHO KNEW THEY COULD\NLOOK SO INNOCENT, THOUGH?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.17,0:23:05.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- I KNOW, THEY LOOK SO ADORABLE.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.51,0:23:07.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- THEY MUST BE TIRED\NAFTER LAST NIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.51,0:23:10.35,Main,,0,0,0,,IT WAS CRAZY.  I'M GLAD EVERYONE\NHAD SUCH A GOOD TIME, THOUGH.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:11.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU KNOW WHAT'S WEIRD?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:13.60,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY FELL ASLEEP\NALMOST IMMEDIATELY.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.68,0:23:14.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- THEY WERE\NSTUMBLING AROUND
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.06,0:23:16.31,Main,,0,0,0,,BEFORE THEY COULD\NEVEN GET IN THE CAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.40,0:23:17.73,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHEN THEY WERE\NEATING BREAKFAST,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:19.15,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY HAD LOTS OF ENERGY,\NBUT, LIKE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:20.78,Main,,0,0,0,,THE NEXT SECOND,\NTHEY WERE ALL FALLING OVER.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.86,0:23:23.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- THEY WERE JUST REALLY\NEXCITED ABOUT EATING, I GUESS.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.36,0:23:25.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, SERIOUSLY,\NBUT THAT DIDN'T MEAN
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.20,0:23:26.87,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY HAD TO EAT\NALL OF OUR FOOD TOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:28.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT KIND OF SUCKS\NWE DON'T GET
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.37,0:23:29.95,Main,,0,0,0,,TO CHAT WITH THEM\NON THE WAY BACK.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:31.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- I AGREE.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:35.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( groans )\N- THEY FELL ASLEEP SO FAST,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:37.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I DIDN'T GET THE CHANCE TO ASK\NHOW THEY LIKED BREAKFAST.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.13,0:23:39.88,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY DON'T EVEN KNOW\NI WAS THE ONE WHO MADE IT.
